    public interface Resource
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Res Mult
    • Is Protected
    • Is Active
    • Base Property
    • Base Instance Specification
    • Base Classifier
    • Base Lifeline
    • Base Connectable Element

    See Also:
    GRMPackage.getResource()
